data.description: Welcome to Pernitas point in Live Oak County. This property resides 1 block from Lake Corpus Christi were you can enjoy the views from the two large balconies that overlook the water. Enjoy the amenities that the lake provides with recreational boating, skiing, and local fishing. Come add your personal touches to this home and enjoy.
